name: graphic-art LoRA
description:
About this model

This is a LoRA extracted with permission from pmejna's fantastic graphic-art model. This was extracted against SD 2.1 768, at dim 300 and float16. Results versus the graphic-art checkpoint are similar but not identical when used with SD 2.1 768.

I may extract a higher dim version to see if it works better than this version. Well, that gave me an error, so maybe not.

Copyrights, Licensing and support
If you like this LoRA and pmejna's original model and you want to support their current and upcoming projects: here is their coffee jar

As pmejna has mentioned on their other models - you can use it. Just keep in mind that they spent their money and time to make it. So if you like it, go give them your support! :)
The only restriction is selling their models.

Installation:
Simply put this LoRA model in the models/lora folder of your SD installation.

Versions:

There is one version of this model so far. No keyword - you can use it however you like. This is the alpha version.
